'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4044] on 17 May 2001 at 10:56:03 pm'!"Change Set:		AllocFormTweak-arDate:			17 May 2001Author:			Andreas RaabMake Form>>allocateForm: include endianess of the receiver so that we have a good match when caching against display."!!Form methodsFor: 'initialize-release' stamp: 'ar 5/17/2001 22:54'!allocateForm: extentPoint	"Allocate a new form which is similar to the receiver and can be used for accelerated blts"	^Form extent: extentPoint depth: self nativeDepth! !